BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Frosé Fridays
DTSTART:20260410T000000
DTEND:20260410T000000
UID:1ec015aabc88ae56806a91a93ef9889d@adoberoadwines.com
DESCRIPTION:With all this warm weather lately\, we’ve got the perfect th
 ing for you to cool off with at our Tasting Room in Downtown Petaluma. Our
  winemaker\, Garrett Martin\, has crafted a refreshing new Frosé (frozen 
 rosé) made from our very own 2024 Sonoma County Rosé . We hope you love 
 it! Join us every Friday to enjoy a glass of frosé or any of our other aw
 ard-winning wines in the heart of Petaluma. Whether you’re exploring win
 e country\, planning a weekend outing\, or looking for the best frosé in 
 Sonoma County\, Adobe Road Winery is your go-to destination. Even better\,
  Inside Track Wine Club members enjoy additional club member pricing as we
 ll. Our frosé is available on Fridays\, while supplies last. Walk-ins wel
 come\, reservations recommended. Call or text (707) 774-6699 or use Tock t
 o reserve online.
LOCATION:Adobe Road Tasting Room\, 6 Petaluma Blvd. N - Suite A1 Petaluma\
 , CA
URL:https://adoberoadwines.com/events/frose-fridays/
X-SOURCE:Adobe Road Winery
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:April Friday Happy Hour
DTSTART:20260410T000000
DTEND:20260410T000000
UID:07edbdf4f4725e6d4b41c51a9c486481@adoberoadwines.com
DESCRIPTION:Start your weekend off right! Join us every Friday in April fo
 r Happy Hour at Adobe Road Winery in Downtown Petaluma. Enjoy special 10% 
 off pricing on wines by the glass from 3:30 PM to 5:30 PM. Stop by before 
 going to dinner\, a movie or show! Even better\, Inside Track Wine Club me
 mbers enjoy additional club member pricing as well. Walk-ins welcome\, cal
 l (707) 774-6699 or use Tock for reservations.
LOCATION:Adobe Road Tasting Room\, 6 Petaluma Blvd. N - Suite A1 Petaluma\
 , CA
URL:https://adoberoadwines.com/events/april-friday-happy-hour/
X-SOURCE:Adobe Road Winery
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Live Music – David Correa
DTSTART:20260411T000000
DTEND:20260411T000000
UID:f4419644caf8ffd0dbcb13d4e116274e@adoberoadwines.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special Saturday acoustic live music set at Adob
 e Road Winery in Downtown Petaluma . Sip on award-winning wines while enjo
 ying talented local musicians in a warm and inviting atmosphere. Choose fr
 om wines by the glass or bottle to discover new favorites. Reserve your sp
 ot on Tock and make it a memorable night of great music\, fine wine\, and 
 good company! David Correa is a celebrated guitarist and composer blending
  Latin rhythms with Spanish and world music influences. Since 1999\, The D
 avid Correa Group has built a loyal fanbase across the Bay Area and beyond
  with energetic\, rhythm-driven performances. The group has toured extensi
 vely throughout the western U.S. and earned multiple accolades\, including
  three consecutive NORBAY Awards for Best Latin Band. Correa has released 
 seven albums\, including New Moon and Alta Vista \, and has been featured 
 alongside New Flamenco greats like Ottmar Liebert and Jesse Cook. His live
  shows promise a vibrant mix of soulful guitar\, rhythm\, and musical stor
 ytelling.
LOCATION:Adobe Road Tasting Room\, 6 Petaluma Blvd. N - Suite A1 Petaluma\
 , CA
URL:https://adoberoadwines.com/events/live-music-david-correa-april-11-202
 6/
X-SOURCE:Adobe Road Winery
END:VEVENT
