BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Live Music – Mike Z
DTSTART:20260425T000000
DTEND:20260425T000000
UID:473548902ee17687582ad42e98e5c3f7@adoberoadwines.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special Saturday acoustic live music set at Adob
 e Road Winery in Downtown Petaluma . Sip on award-winning wines while enjo
 ying talented local musicians in a warm and inviting atmosphere. Choose fr
 om wines by the glass or bottle to discover new favorites. Reserve your sp
 ot on Tock and make it a memorable night of great music\, fine wine\, and 
 good company! Born and raised in San Francisco\, Mike Z joined his first 
 “working” band in high school. Although he started as a trumpet player
  (which he gave up because he couldn’t talk\, let alone sing\, while pla
 ying)\, he switched to bass\, and then guitar. Playing in Bay Area bands e
 arly in his career\, he had the opportunity to back such acts as The Whisp
 ers\, The Pointer Sisters\, and Johnny Taylor. Mike Z has written original
  tunes for film and TV libraries\, and performed on numerous studio tracks
 . Mike Z appears currently in the bands Z and The Benders and the Mike Z J
 azz Trio.
LOCATION:Adobe Road Tasting Room\, 6 Petaluma Blvd. N - Suite A1 Petaluma\
 , CA
URL:https://adoberoadwines.com/events/live-music-mike-z-april-25-2026/
X-SOURCE:Adobe Road Winery
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Downtown Petaluma Spring Antique Faire
DTSTART:20260426T000000
DTEND:20260426T000000
UID:face474d43d7ba10de2ca2a061a2d58a@adoberoadwines.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the 2026 Spring Antique Faire \, one of Downtown P
 etaluma’s annual flagship community events! Over 8\,000 collectors visit
  this marketplace event taking place on Kentucky Street\, just steps away 
 from our tasting room . Between shopping\, relax with a glass of our award
 -winning wine\, or enjoy a curated wine tasting as you enjoy one of Petalu
 ma’s best weekends to visit. The event is 8:00 AM to 4:00 PM. Our tastin
 g room is open 11:00 AM to 7:00 PM. We hope to see you at the Downtown Pet
 aluma Spring Antique Faire!
LOCATION:Adobe Road Tasting Room\, 6 Petaluma Blvd. N - Suite A1 Petaluma\
 , CA
URL:https://adoberoadwines.com/events/downtown-petaluma-spring-antique-fai
 re/
X-SOURCE:Adobe Road Winery
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Salute to American Graffiti Car Show
DTSTART:20260516T000000
DTEND:20260516T000000
UID:727389f4fabd4c6cf1a6b3f666326a9f@adoberoadwines.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us in downtown Petaluma for one of our most beloved homet
 own events — Salute to American Graffiti Car Show & Cruisin’ the Boule
 vard ! This annual celebration honors Petaluma’s role in George Lucas’
  iconic 1973 film American Graffiti and brings over 600 classic American c
 ars back to the same streets where the movie was filmed. Walk the boulevar
 d and enjoy the cars on display. The big cruise starts at 4:00 PM. This no
 stalgic event draws car lovers from all over to enjoy retro era cars and p
 op culture. While you’re visiting the event\, stop by the Adobe Road Win
 ery tasting room for a glass of wine — we have front row seats to the ac
 tion. See you in downtown Petaluma!
LOCATION:Adobe Road Tasting Room\, 6 Petaluma Blvd. N - Suite A1 Petaluma\
 , CA
URL:https://adoberoadwines.com/events/american-graffiti-car-show/
X-SOURCE:Adobe Road Winery
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
